| Severity | Count | Top Issue |
|----------|-------|-----------|
| 🔴 Critical | 2 | `string.Split` + LINQ per call — compound 5+ allocations on every truncation |
| 🟡 Moderate | 4 | Triple-alloc right-truncation, `List<char>` linear scan, unsealed classes |
| ℹ️ Info | 0 | — |

